      "autoSync": false,
      "theme": "dark",
      "code": "flowchart LR\n    classDef critical fill:#7f1d1d,stroke:#fecaca,color:#fee2e2,stroke-width:2px\n    classDef service fill:#0b3b5a,stroke:#7dd3fc,color:#e0f2fe\n    classDef store fill:#14532d,stroke:#86efac,color:#dcfce7\n\n    subgraph Client[Client Channels]\n      WEB[Web App]\n      MOB[Mobile App]\n      API[Partner API]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Edge[Edge Layer]\n      GW[API Gateway]\n      WAF[WAF / Rate Limit]\n      AUTH[Auth Service]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Core[Core Domain]\n      ORCH[Order Orchestrator]\n      INV[Inventory Service]\n      PAY[Payment Service]\n      SHIP[Shipment Service]\n      NOTIF[Notification Service]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Data[Data & Events]\n      ODB[(Orders DB)]\n      IDB[(Inventory DB)]\n      BUS[(Event Bus)]\n      DLQ[(Dead Letter Queue)]\n    end\n\n    WEB --> GW\n    MOB --> GW\n    API --> GW\n    GW --> WAF --> AUTH --> ORCH\n\n    ORCH --> INV\n    ORCH --> PAY\n    ORCH --> SHIP\n\n    INV --> IDB\n    ORCH --> ODB\n\n    ORCH -- publish --> BUS\n    PAY -- payment.failed --> BUS\n    SHIP -- shipment.created --> BUS\n    BUS --> NOTIF\n    BUS -. poison message .-> DLQ\n\n    PAY -- rollback reserve --> INV\n    INV -- out_of_stock --> ORCH\n\n    class PAY,DLQ critical\n    class GW,AUTH,ORCH,INV,SHIP,NOTIF service\n    class ODB,IDB,BUS,DLQ store"
    },
