      "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    state \"Alert Received\" as AlertReceived\n    state \"On-call Triaging\" as Triaging\n    state \"Mitigation In Progress\" as Mitigating\n    state \"Rollback Deploy\" as Rollback\n    state \"Throttle Traffic\" as Throttle\n    state \"Regional Failover\" as Failover\n    state \"Verification\" as Verification\n    state \"Postmortem Draft\" as Postmortem\n    state \"Action Items Tracking\" as ActionItems\n    state \"Closed\" as Closed\n\n    AlertReceived --> Triaging : pager acknowledged\n    Triaging --> Mitigating : impact confirmed\n    Triaging --> Closed : false positive\n\n    Mitigating --> Rollback : bad release suspected\n    Mitigating --> Throttle : traffic spike\n    Mitigating --> Failover : region unhealthy\n\n    Rollback --> Verification : deployment reverted\n    Throttle --> Verification : limits applied\n    Failover --> Verification : failover completed\n\n    Verification --> Mitigating : errors still elevated\n    Verification --> Postmortem : service stable\n    Postmortem --> ActionItems : root cause confirmed\n    ActionItems --> Closed : owners and due dates assigned\n\n    Triaging : severity matrix and blast radius\n    Verification : check SLO, latency and saturation"
    },
