      "code": "timeline\n    title Enterprise Platform Rollout (12 Months)\n\n    section Foundation\n      Jan-Feb : Landing zone hardening : SSO + baseline observability\n      Mar     : Service catalog bootstrap : Team ownership model\n\n    section Migration Waves\n      Apr-May : Wave 1 (low-risk services) : Canary and automated rollback\n      Jun-Jul : Wave 2 (stateful workloads) : Dual-write and CDC validation\n      Aug-Sep : Wave 3 (customer-critical paths) : Error budget guardrails\n\n    section Governance\n      Oct     : Security posture review : Threat modeling refresh\n      Nov     : Compliance evidence automation : Audit dry run\n\n    section Business Readiness\n      Dec     : FinOps optimization : Unit economics checkpoint\n      Dec     : Executive go/no-go : 2027 scale plan"
